<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Bulk Making Time</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --color-bg-primary: #f7f9fb;
      --color-surface: #ffffff;
      --color-border: #dce4ed;
      --color-text-primary: #1b2838;
      --color-text-secondary: #4b5563;
      --color-text-muted: #6b7280;
      --color-accent: #0f52ba;
      --color-accent-soft: #e9f0ff;
      --color-success: #0f9d58;
      --color-danger: #d60036;
      --shadow-md: 0 14px 24px rgba(15, 82, 186, 0.08);
      --shadow-soft: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    body {
      background: var(--color-bg-primary);
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .navbar {
      background: var(--color-surface) !important;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--color-text-primary) !important;
    }

    .navbar-brand i { color: var(--color-accent); }

    .page-lede {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 82, 186, 0.08), rgba(15, 82, 186, 0.02));
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .card-body { padding: 1.5rem; }

    .badge-soft {
      background: var(--color-accent-soft);
      color: var(--color-accent);
      border: 1px solid #d0dcf0;
    }

    textarea {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SFMono-Regular', Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    }

    .helper-list { color: var(--color-text-muted); }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--color-accent);
      border-color: var(--color-accent);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 18px rgba(15, 82, 186, 0.25);
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .btn-outline-secondary {
      border-color: var(--color-border);
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .summary-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--color-accent-soft);
      color: var(--color-accent);
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .card-body { padding: 1.1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center" href="/easyecom/stock-market">
        <i class="bi bi-bar-chart me-2"></i> Inventory stock market
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <div class="page-lede mb-4">
      <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-md-center justify-content-between gap-3">
        <div>
          <p class="text-uppercase text-muted fw-bold small mb-1">Bulk update</p>
          <h3 class="fw-bold mb-1">Set making time in bulk</h3>
          <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Paste CSV style rows to quickly align making time with stock market targets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
          <a href="/easyecom/stock-market" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Back to stock market</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-lg-7">
            <h6 class="text-uppercase text-muted fw-bold mb-3">Paste rows</h6>
            <p class="text-muted">Format each line as <span class="badge badge-soft">SKU, Warehouse(optional), Making Time (days)</span>.</p>
            <div class="alert alert-info">
              Examples: <code>SKU123, WH1, 5</code> or <code>SKU123,,7</code> for a default warehouse entry.
            </div>

            <% if (result && result.errors.length) { %>
              <div class="alert alert-danger">
                <strong>Some rows failed:</strong>
                <ul class="mb-0">
                  <% result.errors.forEach(err => { %>
                    <li><%= err %></li>
                  <% }); %>
                </ul>
              </div>
            <% } %>
            <% if (result && result.success.length) { %>
              <div class="alert alert-success d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                <span>Updated <strong><%= result.success.length %></strong> row(s).</span>
                <span class="summary-pill"><%= result.success.join(', ') %></span>
              </div>
            <% } %>

            <form method="post" action="/easyecom/stock-market/making-time">
              <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="bulkInput" class="form-label fw-semibold">Bulk input</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" id="bulkInput" name="bulkInput" rows="10" placeholder="SKU123, WH1, 5&#10;SKU456,,7" required><%= bulkInput || '' %></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Update making time</button>
                <span class="text-muted small">Changes apply immediately to replenishment rules.</span>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-5">
            <h6 class="text-uppercase text-muted fw-bold mb-3">Helpful hints</h6>
            <ul class="helper-list ps-3">
              <li class="mb-2">Use uppercase SKUs for consistency with stock market tables.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">Leave warehouse empty to set a default making time.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">Double-check day values are numbers; invalid rows are skipped with errors.</li>
              <li class="mb-2">After updating, refresh the stock market view to see the latest runway and momentum.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
</body>
</html>
